</li>
<li id="cite_note-34"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Hadith are primarily from Muhammad but some are from those closest to him. Muslim scholars have worked carefully to authenticate them.</span>
</li>
